WEBVTT

00:03:29.469 --> 00:03:32.794
All I want you to do
is integrate that Navy."

00:03:33.675 --> 00:03:36.112
And that was what Franklin did.

00:03:36.136 --> 00:03:38.136
Well, Franklin didn't live to do it,

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:39.816
but Truman did it.

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:42.438
But when this woman told me,

00:03:42.462 --> 00:03:45.621
"I have flown everything there is to fly,"

00:03:45.645 --> 00:03:49.238
bombers, just all kinds of planes,

00:03:49.262 --> 00:03:52.603
it just melted me, you know,

00:03:52.627 --> 00:03:55.647
just to see how far women have come.

00:03:55.671 --> 00:03:56.913
And I told her, I said,

00:03:56.937 --> 00:04:00.105
